Item 5.   Other Events and Regulation FD Disclosure
On January 15, 2004, A. O. Smith Corporation ("the Company") issued a news release announcing that Dennis J. Martin was elected to the Board of Directors. A copy of the Company's news release is attached as Exhibit 99 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (this "Current Report") and is incorporated by reference herein.
