A. O. Smith elects Jones to board of directors
         A. O. Smith Corporation (AOS-NYSE) today announced that President and Chief Operating Officer Paul W. Jones has been elected to its Board of Directors.
Milwaukee, Wis.
        Jones was named president of the Milwaukee-based manufacturer of electric motors and water heaters in January 2004 with responsibility for its Electrical Products and Water Systems operations worldwide as well as its Corporate Technology Center.
