Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
On January 22, 2007, A. O. Smith Corporation ("the Company") issued a news release announcing the Company's 2006 earnings. A copy of the Company's news release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (this "Current Report") and is incorporated by reference herein.
