On July 17, 2008, A. O. Smith Corporation ("the Company") issued a news release announcing the Company's second quarter earnings. A copy of the Company's news release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (this "Current Report") and is incorporated by reference herein.
 
The following exhibit is being filed herewith:
(99.1)    News Release of A. O. Smith Corporation, dated July 17, 2008.
 
