On July 20, 2010, A. O. Smith Corporation ("the Company") issued a news release announcing the Company's second quarter earnings. A copy of the Company's news release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (this "Current Report") and is incorporated by reference herein.
 
