product, material practice, condition or other circumstances claimed to have caused the alleged injury, and the numerator of which shall be such claiming U.S. Transferred Employee's total length of exposure, which in the case of calculating the Seller's Liability is the time prior to the Effective Time, and for calculating the Buyer's Liability the time following the Effective Time.
