A. O. Smith Corporation (the "Company") announced that it and Regal Beloit Corporation ("RBC") have each received a second request for information from the Antitrust Division of the United States Department of Justice under the Hart-Scott-Rodino Antitrust Improvements Act of 1976. The request relates to the pending disposition of the Company's electric motors business to RBC.
A copy of the Company's news release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K (this "Current Report") and is incorporated by reference herein.
 
